\u00e9\u00e2tre de Luxembourg]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 1973|1973]], [[Eurovision Song Contest 1984|1984]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"13\"| 3\n|rowspan=\"2\"| {{FRA}}\n| [[Cannes]]\n| [[Palais des Festivals et des Congr\u00e8s|Palais des Festivals]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 1959|1959]], [[Eurovision Song Contest 1961|1961]] \n|-\n| [[Paris]]\n| [[Palais des congr\u00e8s de Paris|Palais des Congr\u00e8s]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 1978|1978]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|{{NOR}}\n| [[Bergen]]\n| [[Grieghallen]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 1986|1986]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Oslo]]\n| [[Oslo Spektrum]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 1996|1996]]\n|-\n| [[Telenor Arena]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 2010|2010]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"| {{GER}}{{efn|The 1957 and 1983 contests were held in what was then [[West Germany]]. The 2011 contest was in reunified Germany.}}\n| [[Frankfurt|Frankfurt-am-Main]]\n| [[Gro\u00dfer Sendesaal des hessischen Rundfunks|Gro\u00dfer Sendesaal]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 1957|1957]]\n|-\n| [[Munich]]\n| [[Rudi-Sedlmayer-Halle]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 1983|1983]]\n|-\n| [[D\u00fcsseldorf]]\n| [[Esprit Arena]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 2011|2011]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"| {{DEN}}\n|rowspan=\"3\"| [[Copenhagen]]\n| [[Tivolis Koncertsal]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 1964|1964]]\n|-\n| [[Parken|Parken Stadium]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 2001|2001]]\n|-\n| [[B&W Hallerne]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 2014|2014]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"| {{ISR}}\n|rowspan=\"1\"| [[Jerusalem]]\n| [[International Convention Center (Jerusalem)|International Convention Centre]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 1979|1979]], [[Eurovision Song Contest 1999|1999]]\n|-\n| [[Tel Aviv]]\n| [[Expo Tel Aviv]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 2019|2019]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"8\"| 2\n|rowspan=\"2\"| {{SUI}}\n| [[Lugano]]\n| [[Teatro Kursaal]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 1956|1956]]\n|-\n| [[Lausanne]]\n| [[Palais de Beaulieu]]\n| [[Eurovision Song Contest 1989|1989]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|{{ITA}}\n| [