ry and redundant to include the remix as well. -->\n| chronology = [[Lizzo]] singles\n| prev_title = [[Tempo (Lizzo song)|Tempo]]\n| prev_year = 2019\n| next_title = [[Cuz I Love You (song)|Cuz I Love You]]\n| next_year = 2020\n| misc = {{Extra chronology\n| artist = [[Ariana Grande]] singles\n| type = single\n| prev_title = [[Don't Call Me Angel]]\n| prev_year  = 2019\n| title      = Good as Hell (Remix)\n| year       = 2019\n| next_title = \n| next_year  =\n}}{{External music video|1={{YouTube|WIBwOmCKhE4|\"Good as Hell (Remix)\"}}|header=Lyric video|type=single}}\n}}\nA remix of the song featuring American singer [[Ariana Grande]] was released on October 25, 2019.<ref name=\"iTunes\"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/lizzo/status/1187801799178121216|via=Twitter|title=Lizzo on Twitter|date=October 25, 2019}}</ref>\n\n===Track listing===\n'''Digital download'''<ref name=iTunes>{{cite web|title=Good as Hell (Remix) [feat. Ariana Grande] - Single by Lizzo|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/good-as-hell-remix-feat-ariana-grande-single/1484536033|website=[[Apple Music]]|accessdate=October 26, 2019}}</ref>\n# \"Good as Hell\" (featuring [[Ariana Grande]]) [Remix] \u2013 2:39\n\n'''Streaming'''<ref>{{cite web|url= https://open.spotify.com/album/1k1HuvFs562Z3CCiSYhtc1?si=RvS-wDEtQYilMErm3SlrHQ|title=Good As Hell (feat. Ariana Grande) [Remix]|website=[[Spotify]]|accessdate=October 26, 2019}}</ref>\n# \"Good as Hell\" (featuring Ariana Grande) - Remix \u2013 2:39\n# \"Good as Hell\" \u2013 2:39\n\n===Accolades===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"width: 60%;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Ceremony\n! scope=\"col\" | Category\n! scope=\"col\" | Result\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\"| {{Abbr|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" |2020\n| [[iHeartRadio Music Awards]]\n| Best Remix\n| {{pending}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{Cite news |url=https://news.iheart.com/featured/iheartradio-music-awards/content/2020-0